text:
Man, I was initially worried about the trip. But bhai tum dono ke bina itna maza nahi ho paata. One of the best parts of the trip was knowing you two! Be it that night of Social Humour or our way back from Sagnik's cocktail disaster, it all was fun, truly fun! Wish we could have had more laughs and time together (another trip?).

P.S.: Turned out Hookah harms too. Lungs barbaad BC;-;
